# gcs_rust workspace

- Layout: crates live under `crates/<name>`; register each in root `Cargo.toml` `[workspace].members`.
- Shared path deps go in `[workspace.dependencies]` (e.g. `rtcm3_parser`).
- RTCM framing/CRC only in `rtcm3_parser`; MSM and emulator business logic stay in `rtk_base_emulator`.
- Do not reimplement CRC-24Q or RTCM frame wrapping outside `rtcm3_parser`.
- Prefer `edition.workspace = true` and `license.workspace = true` in member `Cargo.toml`.
- Domain comments/logs in Russian; code identifiers in English.
- Validate with `cargo fmt --all` and `cargo test --workspace`.
